## Goals

The Composure Quick Start Guide aims to quickly get you up and running with the basics to compositing cinematics in Unreal Engine 4. 

If you are completely new to Composure, this guide is for you! 

## Objectives

After going through this tutorial, developers will know the following:

*	How to enable the needed Composure Plugins.
*	How to setup a scene to be used with Composure.
*	How to setup the Composure Blueprints.
* 	How to create a shot that uses Composure. 


